text: Playa Blanca Marine Wetland (Blanca Beach Marine Wetland, ), is a protected area in Costa Rica, managed under the Central Pacific Conservation Area, it was created in 1994 by decree 23127-MIRENEM. == References == Category:Costa Rica Category:Protected areas Category:Nature reserves in Costa Rica Category:Protected areas established in 1994
title: Playa Blanca Marine Wetland
